      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，预处理之后数据要进入标准化层。B再连到C，C还是PatientRecords，代表清洗后的标准格式。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "B[HealthTech_PatientRecords]",
        "C[HealthTech_PatientRecords]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，B到C的粗箭头已加上。接下来C应该进入合规检查环节了吧？我打算用菱形表示决策点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C[HealthTech_PatientRecords]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错，C后面接HIPAA_Vault，这是我们的合规审查节点。用菱形D表示，通过HIPAA认证的数据才能继续流转。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "D{HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault}"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "D节点已创建为菱形。现在需要分两支：Yes分支走EMR同步，No分支走异常处理。我先画Yes路径？",
      "elements_involved": [
